name: Endbringer Attack - Worm Fangame
description:
Small fangame based loosely on the BrantSteele Hunger Games Simulator featuring the cast and scenarios of the Worm Webserial. Current version is pretty bare bones but might be updated in the future to add a bit more meat. I hope you enjoy :).
